What is the time complexity of the following algorithm that determines whether a given number is a prime number or not?

```
function is_prime(n):
    if n <= 1:
        return False
    for i in range(2, int(n**0.5)+1):
        if n % i == 0:
            return False
    return True
``` 

(Note: Time complexity should be expressed as big O notation)
